text Route_201_Text_Rival_Mentions_Idea
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: All right!\n"
    "Let's get moving to Prof. Rowan's lab."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Explains_Its_Fine
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "What?\n"
    "Don't go into grass, right?\l"
    "No worries! No problem!\p"
    "It doesn't matter that we don't have\n"
    "any Pokémon.\p"
    "Trust me on this one.\n"
    "I've got an idea!\p"
    "Now listen. You know how wild Pokémon\n"
    "jump out when you go into tall grass?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Explains_More
{
    "So, what you do is, you scoot over to\n"
    "the next patch of grass before any\l"
    "wild Pokémon can appear!\p"
    "If we just keep dashing, we can get to\n"
    "Sandgem Town without running into\l"
    "wild Pokémon!\p"
    "Ok, stick with me!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Talk_Before_Running
{
    "Ok, here goes!\p"
    "On your marks..."    
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Says_Hold
{
    "Hold it!"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Tells_We_Are_Fools
{
    "Professor: You two don't seem to have\n"
    "any Pokémon between you?\p"
    "Then, what is the meaning of going into\n"
    "the tall grass?!\p"
    "{PLAYER}: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "Professor: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "...\n"
    "..."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rival_Realize_Its_Rowan
{
    "{B_RIVAL_NAME}: Hey, {PLAYER}.\n"
    "This old guy...\p"
    "It's Prof. Rowan isn't it?\n"
    "What's he doing here...?"
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Thinks
{
    "Professor: ...\n"
    "...\p"
    "They tried to go into the tall grass\n"
    "because they wanted Pokémon...\p"
    "Hmm...\n"
    "What to do...?\p"
    "Their world would surely change if\n"
    "they were to meet Pokémon...\p"
    "Is it right for me to put them on that\n"
    "path...?\p"
    "...\n"
    "..."
}

text Route_201_Text_Rowan_Asks
{
    "You two.\n"
    "You truly love Pokémon, do you?"
}

